工又低<br />\n球會無歷史</blockquote><br />\n好似你隊波咁咩,個個為錢黎踢<br />\n你點介定有無歷史先?你隊波好有歷史??<br />\n其實我本身又唔太憎你地隊波(因為孫繼海)<br />\n但你呢條勝利球迷影撚蕭衰晒你隊波</blockquote><br />\n傻西先會以為球員為錢踢<br />\n用屎眼睇野架你？我咪話左永世無冠軍<br />\n得你以為下下講錢<br />\n同埋我又無話自己隊波有歷史<br />\n但起碼有冠軍，唔似熱狗無冠又打人"},{"pid":"e010c7f74cc4c3737992b0033b9d748d83d07267","tid":190382,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:10:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>忽然覺得安利陳要10萬鎊好抵🤣</blockquote><br />\n兩個都係垃圾</blockquote><br />\n又狙"},{"pid":"adcb9faf2e167b729bd444e95b999c4e945f3999","tid":190382,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:10:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牛餐吃什麼</blockquote><br />\n日本野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你地利記今年前四了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無<br />\n你地都無但拎歐霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72196e900c203b952b1735a56a49bd51823ebdf4","tid":190382,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:11:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;LIN</blockquote><br />\n真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nall&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;樓主&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;LIN["},{"pid":"61e2f8982d0f59f5fc324468fbfcf4350f9c1a27","tid":190382,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0